Class Matrix

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.math.matrix.Matrix
All Implemented Interfaces:
Grid<Double>, NumericGrid<Double,Matrix>, Serializable, Iterable<Double>
public class Matrix extends Object implements NumericGrid<Double,Matrix>
A two-dimensional grid of doubles.

    • isIdentity

      public boolean isIdentity()
      Returns whether this matrix is an identity matrix. This is achieved by first checking if this matrix is a square matrix, then checking if all diagonal components are 1 and every non-diagonal component is 0. If all conditions hold, this return true.
      Returns:
      true if this matrix is an identity matrix
